item.title: The 2010s - Part 2
item.description: This is 2ndinstallment of the story. I’m trying to arrange beautiful photos of the last decade. The photos are all captured by me. The foggy view of training center on a December morning. The first time I had a taste of resort-like place. 2011 - The Training Days The Kevin Mitnick replied and followed me, after a tweet about Ghost in the Wires Kevin Mitnick follows me This was one only outreach programme that I took part in.
